- How to start the game

  With all the files in this archive in the current directory, run charge.bat to start the game.
  You should be able to quit the game by pressing esc while in game.

------------------------------ chika1995 ---

- Game Description

  Control your ship (Player 1 is red/Player 2 is blue) and attack the enemy.
  When an attack hits an enemy, the enemy's energy decreases, 
  and if the enemy's energy reaches 0, you win the first round.
  Round 2 The first player to win can move on to the next round.

  Since you can join in on the fun with other players, it's a good idea to invite lots of friends to play.

  There are two types of attacks for your aircraft:
  - FrameSword (fired with trigger A) The range is short, but the power is great.
				Available when the charge meter is yellow or green
  - Power Laser (fired with Trigger B) Has a long range but low power.
				Only available when the charge meter is green

